          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1632303455367-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chipotle stock</strong>, <strong>drained black beans </strong>and<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) to the pan and bring to the boil</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>spicy meat-free mince chilli</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632303465083-x200.jpg",
