            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s] </strong>using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and dice roughly</p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Crumble your<strong> feta</strong> into large pieces using your hands</p><p>Cut your<strong> lime[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632303492569-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632303492569-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632303492569-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632303492569-x1000.jpg",
