          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632303492569-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> diced avocado</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion </strong>and<strong> crumbled feta</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime[s] </strong>and stir it all together – this is your<strong> feta & avocado salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1632303506970-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
